  },
  "name": "0222 GoogleSheets Readbinaryfile Automate",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from Danitilahun/n8n-workflow-templates: 0222 GoogleSheets Readbinaryfile Automate",
  "category": "Data",
  "tags": [
    "workflows",
